## 11. UI Requirements

### 11.1 Patient List Page

The page should contain:

* Search field
* Filter options
* Add patient button
* Patient number
* Patient name
* Age and gender
* Mobile number
* Last visit
* Upcoming appointment
* Status
* Action menu
* Pagination

### 11.2 Patient Registration Page

Sections:

1. Basic information
2. Contact details
3. Address
4. Emergency contact
5. Basic medical information
6. Consent acknowledgement

The page should support:

* Inline validation
* Duplicate warnings
* Save and continue
* Cancel
* Registration source selection
* Mobile-friendly layout

### 11.3 Patient Profile Page

Suggested layout:

```text
Patient Header
├── Name
├── Patient Number
├── Age / Gender
├── Mobile
├── Status
└── Edit Action

Profile Tabs
├── Overview
├── Timeline
├── Appointments
├── Consultations
├── Prescriptions
├── Lab Reports
├── Billing
└── Documents
```

### 11.4 Patient Timeline Page

The timeline should:

* Display newest events first by default
* Allow chronological sorting
* Support filtering
* Show event source
* Show doctor or staff member
* Provide links to permitted details

### 11.5 Patient Portal Profile

The patient portal should display:

* Personal information
* Upcoming appointments
* Recent prescriptions
* Recent lab reports
* Pending payments
* Profile-update action

