# Document Summary

The Patient Management module provides the central patient identity and record required by all major Clinora workflows.

It enables secure registration, search, profile management, patient timelines, document management and patient self-service while enforcing tenant isolation, role-based access and detailed auditing.

The next recommended document is:

```text
12_Doctor_Management_And_Scheduling_PRD_v1.0.docx
```

That document should define doctor profiles, clinic associations, consultation fees, working schedules, breaks, holidays, leave, appointment-slot generation and doctor availability.
